name: Victorious Maokai
description: Victorious Maokai was awarded to players who reached Gold or higher in the 2016 season. Victorious Maokai lays down his roots fashionably with vines of golden leaves, and a rich blue and gold robe.

wikiSkinData.distribution: Reward for finishing the ranked season in Gold or higher.
